[{"index":1,"title":"【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"<a href=\"\"  onclick=\"Stats.sendRequest('fr=tb0_forum&st_mod=pb&st_value=atlink');\" onmouseover=\"showattip(this)\" onmouseout=\"hideattip(this)\" username=\"%D1%BE%BC%A7\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"at\">@丫姬</a>  我说的聘礼其实是诗╮（￣▽￣）╭请收下吧","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:38","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"夜宿荒寺问<br>路过汝之城，犹忆画中人。<br>窄巷烟迟暗，长街蔺先焜。<br>楼外木萧萧，溪傍柳纷纷。<br>秋风撩竹伞，夜雨褪新尘。<br>携雨过孤桥，燃香祭庙神。<br>旧阁蛛网连，堂下烛油冷。<br>桌台拾香纸，御笔寄离人。<br>不觉打更声，残窗见月轮。<br>雨过风卷絮，来路乱泥痕。<br>望月思难断，倚门自相问。<br>苍蝶何处去？棕缕几时闻？<br>蓝羽归不归？黑珠辗转分？<br>橙簪仍旧粲？他年聚银樽？<br>夜半灯不答，独闻乌啼恨。","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:40","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"这是我向你求组cp那天写的，下面的是刚完工的","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:42","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"路过你的城 为寻画中人<br>在城外的黄昏<br>流光余下氤氲的烟粉<br>残阳看我推开半掩的城门","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:43","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"行过画楼幡幕泛灰<br>途经街市桌案染尘<br>晚霞为塔庙披上华盖<br>却不见炊烟升起","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:43","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"亭台的阶上堆满落花<br>余晖抚过寂寞的城","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:44","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":7,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"杨柳下斑驳蓝裙<br>浣女在河畔洗砧","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:45","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":8,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"你的身影偶现，<br>在窄巷里穿行<br>拾起橘色的发簪<br>眼眸闪烁微弱而明亮的光<br>是小小希翼","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:46","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":9,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"谁和我一般<br>在萧瑟中一遍遍回忆忘不了的流年<br>灿烂如日落的城<br>谁和我一般<br>在古都里一次次徘徊于旧日的长街<br>哀伤如藤蔓延伸","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:46","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":10,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"谁不舍昔日冷面少女掌中刃<br>谁企盼策马而归的陨落之臣<br>谁惦念她久违的笑颜暖胜阳春<br>谁静待黑发女孩与他相认","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:47","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":11,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"谁不甘心地拨弄风铃<br>谁习惯了这苦等","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:48","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":12,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"谁守候着繁华落尽的城<br>谁不悔邂逅那画，那人","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:49","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":13,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"我调转青驴，<br>愿羁留于此<br>与蝶，与莲，与你比邻而居<br>在夜色的河边掌一盏灯<br>送给感伤的来客暖光一寸","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:49","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":14,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"待青山点黛，江花似火<br>郭外又响起商旅的蹄声<br>谁历经风霜重归<br>执笔写下召文<br>唤醒沉眠的他们","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:50","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":15,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"仿佛回到那个夏天<br>仿佛<br>回到每个你我盼望的晨昏","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:50","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":16,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"祝你在马年在三次元也马上有对象！","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:52","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":17,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"解释一下，在诗里，嘻哈吧=古城<br>苍蝶=冥羽心 棕缕=幻<br>蓝羽=毛小蒙 黑珠=葛琪琪<br>橙簪=gigi 银樽=上官帅","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 14:57","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":18,"title":"回复：【聘礼】 新娘请进","content":"按这个脑洞去想，刘飒就是弃国外逃的昏君，他的几个都城（撞上、嘻哈）都荒废了，呛辣城也没治理好<img class=\"BDE_Smiley\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" changedsize=\"false\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/bjq/image_editoricon29.png\" >","author":"希斯克厉夫林顿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7570477b.Li4GLDbM74lwx0IbGEfwIg?t=1389184148&fr=pb","date":"2014-01-29 15:08","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null}]